applicationModel.name: example-editable-table
applicationModel.description:
This application contains a fully-editable table showing persons working in enterprises. Each person can be edited in-place by clicking on the table rows. Expanding the table row shows more details. Persons are persisted in a storage. A simple search field allows searching the enterprises in the table.
The index page contains a table showing persons (stored in a local storage). The table has editable fields with inputs and selects. It also has a show details feature.
The demo2 page contains a split view showing enterprises stored in a local storage. The left part contains a table, and the right part contains either a graph with computed data, or a map showing the enterprises locations, depending on the user's choice.
The RDV page shows a stepper to make appointments.
The form page shows a stepper with various inputs.
The calendar page shows an example using a calendar plugin.
